    "We identified tasks that have a bad edit as well as a good edit (i.e.",
    "the task was reworked later on such that it follows the provided feedback).",
    "The second type of undesirable edits is when no edit was made (i.e.",
    "the edited response simply copies the original model response).",
    "While this was not seen in the human annotated data, we observed this phenomenon in a substantial fraction of a model trained on the Edit Demonstration dataset."
  ],
